{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-07",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听AI 每日先锋，今天是2026年7月7日。我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 6.269,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。",
      "start": 7.718,
      "duration": 2.395,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "周航你发现没有，今年科技圈有个特别明显的变化，以前大家聊AI动不动就\"千亿参数\"\"万卡集群\"，现在你看新闻，全是什么\"减负\"\"提效\"\"轻量化\"。",
      "start": 10.61,
      "duration": 13.148,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这个拐点其实2025年下半年就开始显现了，Scaling Law的边际效益越来越低，大家发现光堆算力这条路快走到头了。",
      "start": 24.211,
      "duration": 11.45,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，今天咱们聊的几条新闻特别有意思，两个头条一个比一个\"反套路\"。",
      "start": 36.066,
      "duration": 6.313,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说白了，全球AI的底层叙事真的在变。",
      "start": 42.812,
      "duration": 4.31,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那咱直接上硬菜。先说第一个，阿里和清华联合搞了一个扩散模型的推理优化，拿下了ICML的杰出论文。",
      "start": 47.587,
      "duration": 8.229,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个含金量得给听众朋友们强调一下，ICML杰出论文一年就那么几篇，基本上是机器学习领域最受认可的学术荣誉之一了。",
      "start": 56.278,
      "duration": 12.234,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "但我跟你说，最让我惊讶的不是拿奖，是他们用的方法——\"极简\"两个字。",
      "start": 68.963,
      "duration": 5.224,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你听我讲，他们其实是在挑战一个根深蒂固的假设。大家以前做扩散模型推理加速，都是在已有的复杂框架上做修补、加插件、打补丁，搞得越来越重。",
      "start": 74.687,
      "duration": 14.541,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那他们怎么搞的？",
      "start": 89.666,
      "duration": 1.176,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "他们直接把架构推倒重来，用一个极简的设计去做推理，结果速度刷新了纪录，而且效果不打折扣。",
      "start": 91.303,
      "duration": 9.056,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这也太狠了，等于告诉整个行业：你以前那么多\"优化\"，可能本身就是多余的。",
      "start": 100.804,
      "duration": 5.834,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我觉得更深的意义在于工程范式。以前大家信奉\"大力出奇迹\"，参数越大越好，结构越复杂越好，现在这个论文相当于在学术最高舞台上给\"以巧取胜\"正了名。",
      "start": 107.112,
      "duration": 14.933,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "而且你想啊，如果扩散模型能这么省，那以后AIGC内容的生产成本会降一个数量级，做视频、做3D那些以前觉得太贵的应用，马上就能落地了。",
      "start": 122.472,
      "duration": 12.756,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是，这事儿跟我们每个人都有关系。以后刷短视频看到那些特别炫的AI生成内容，成本可能就几毛钱。",
      "start": 135.692,
      "duration": 9.361,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好，第二个头条更有意思，直接搬上联合国了。",
      "start": 145.47,
      "duration": 3.657,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你说的是那个在联合国AI峰会上发言的中国公司吧。",
      "start": 149.563,
      "duration": 4.441,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，他们提了一个特别\"不主流\"的观点——AI不要靠堆算力，而要给机器人装\"类脑\"系统。",
      "start": 154.421,
      "duration": 6.661,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个其实是有产业和地缘两层逻辑的。产业上，现在大家都意识到，Transformer架构这条路快触顶了，不管是能耗还是数据量都跟不上了，必须找新路径。",
      "start": 161.578,
      "duration": 16.588,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，类脑计算其实不是新概念，但这次是中国公司把它摆到联合国桌面上讲。",
      "start": 178.578,
      "duration": 6.487,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "问题是，这时候讲这个，背后有更深的意思。你想啊，AI算力现在基本等于国力，芯片、数据中心、电力，全是大国博弈的焦点。",
      "start": 185.544,
      "duration": 13.235,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "中国这套\"效率优先\"的方案如果被国际采纳，相当于绕开了算力军备竞赛，给发展中国家提供了一条新路。",
      "start": 199.211,
      "duration": 8.403,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错，说白了就是\"我们不跟你在算力上硬刚，我们走另一条道，但这道也能通向AGI\"。",
      "start": 208.082,
      "duration": 8.098,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个叙事很聪明。而且类脑机器人本身也是个万亿级的市场，谁先把标准立起来，谁就掌握话语权。",
      "start": 216.67,
      "duration": 7.793,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这跟咱们刚才说的ICML那篇论文其实是同一个趋势的两面。一个是学术界证明\"小而美\"可行，一个是产业界在外交舞台推动新标准。",
      "start": 224.94,
      "duration": 14.106,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哎，今天聊下来我感觉挺激动的。AI这行当终于不是只有\"越大越好\"这一条路了。",
      "start": 239.464,
      "duration": 6.008,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是，但别太乐观。堆算力那帮人也不会坐以待毙，巨头们肯定还会继续卷参数规模。",
      "start": 245.911,
      "duration": 8.054,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那就让他们卷去，咱们小成本玩家反而有机会了。",
      "start": 254.377,
      "duration": 4.005,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哈，这倒是。说完了两个大头条，过几条快讯吧，轻松一点。",
      "start": 258.875,
      "duration": 5.703,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好，第一条。一个叫OpenSquilla的项目突然冒出来了，0.5.0版本Preview直接登顶了DRACO榜单两个榜。",
      "start": 264.987,
      "duration": 8.664,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个确实挺让人意外。DRACO是那种比较硬核的大模型竞技场，新项目一上来就霸榜不常见。",
      "start": 274.138,
