        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "而且我看他们介绍里提到了一个名字——Fable 5，听着像是他们的旗舰大模型，但具体信息还没披露。",
      "start": 283.2,
      "duration": 8.359,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，这种\"突然冒出来就登顶\"的项目，要么是真有技术突破，要么是榜单测试集正好被它押中了，具体还得看后续。",
      "start": 292.019,
      "duration": 10.493,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，现在大模型赛道的入场券越来越贵了，能在2026年杀出来的新玩家，要么背后有金主，要么技术真的硬。",
      "start": 302.983,
      "duration": 9.361,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "反正咱们盯着看，这种项目一旦Fable 5正式发布，肯定要掀起一波讨论。",
      "start": 312.756,
      "duration": 5.573,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "第二条，2026奇点智能产品大会日程公布了，字节、宇树、阿里、腾讯、百度，40多个产品大佬齐聚。",
      "start": 318.774,
      "duration": 9.927,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个会我看了下嘉宾名单，挺有意思的，宇树这种机器人公司也去了，说明大家意识到，应用层的创新不只是软件，硬件机器人也是大头。",
      "start": 329.156,
      "duration": 12.756,
      "audios": {
